{"data":[{"date":"16:48 06/08","title":"HLV Bayern n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin Boateng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c M.U quan t\u00e2m?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/hlv-kovac-ngoi-khen-jerome-boateng.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Niko Kovac n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Jerome Boateng. Trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Man United trong n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Boateng \u0111\u1eaft kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean TTCN</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin Jerome Boateng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Paris Saint-Germain li\u00ean h\u1ec7. Ch\u00ednh Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich, Karl-Heinz Rummenigge \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n th\u00f4ng tin Man United mu\u1ed1n mua Boateng. Kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c trung v\u1ec7 hi\u1ec7n c\u00f3, HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u1ec1 su\u1ea5t l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. \u0110\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau, M.U s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u00ean t\u1edbi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Niko Kovac n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Jerome Boateng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Niko Kovac n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Jerome Boateng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/hlv-kovac-ngoi-khen-jerome-boateng.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Jerome Boateng \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c M.U \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Kovac b\u00e0ng quan tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBayern m\u1edbi c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi ch\u00ednh M.U t\u1ea1i Munich. H\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 1-0 nh\u1edd pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Javi Martinez ph\u00fat 59. \u1ede \u0111\u00f3, Boateng ch\u01a1i hi\u1ec7p 2 sau khi v\u00e0o s\u00e2n thay Mats Hummels sau gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9 gi\u1ea3i lao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u00e2n d\u1ecbp n\u00e0y, HLV Niko Kovac n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Jerome Boateng. \u201cV\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n Boateng, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u00f4ng tin g\u00ec m\u1edbi\u201d, \u00f4ng chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean. \u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay sau khi v\u00e0o s\u00e2n. T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui khi Boateng \u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi Bayern. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, c\u00f2n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c n\u1eefa.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nBoateng t\u1eebng ch\u01a1i cho Man City trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2010/11 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u. Anh gia nh\u1eadp Bayern t\u1eeb N\u1eeda xanh th\u00e0nh Manchester n\u0103m 2011 v\u00e0 c\u00f9ng h\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh 6 danh hi\u1ec7u t\u1ea1i Bundesliga, 1 t\u1ea1i Champions League. H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Boateng v\u1edbi Bayern c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n t\u1edbi n\u0103m 2021.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Bayern Munich tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/that-bai-vu-mina-mu-chi-50-trieu-bang-mua-nguoi-thay-the-172-193829.html\">Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1ee5 Mina, MU chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-ti-nanh-voi-cac-doi-thu-khong-ngung-voi-vinh-bld-man-utd-172-193823.html\">MU thua b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c Bayern, Mourinho ra t\u1ed1i h\u1eadu th\u01b0 cho gi\u1edbi ch\u1ee7</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/tro-thanh-dong-doi-messi-vidal-len-tieng-cam-on-hum-xam-180-193716.html\">Tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Messi, Vidal l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea3m \u01a1n H\u00f9m x\u00e1m</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-duc/zambrano-phat-bieu-ve-tan-binh-bayern-alphonso-davies-193-193707.html\">Bayern c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f3n h\u1eddi tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-chinh-thuc-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-sao-khung-bayern-munich-180-193675.html\">Barca CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng sao kh\u1ee7ng Bayern Munich</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/bayern-khong-muon-mua-martial-172-193655.html\">Bayern t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i thanh l\u00fd sao v\u00f4 k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt gi\u00fap M.U</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2063","checkdouble":"193857"},{"date":"16:30 06/08","title":"X\u00e1c nh\u1eadn: Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea quan t\u00e2m \"h\u00e0ng hot\" Bundesliga","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/xac-nhan-arsenal-va-chelsea-quan-tam-leon-bailey.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Leon Bailey n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Bayer Leverkusen kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea quan t\u00e2m Leon Bailey</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Leon Bailey \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Bayer Leverkusen. Ng\u00f4i sao 20 tu\u1ed5i ghi 12 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 7 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng. Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t Bundesliga \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Leon Bailey n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea quan t\u00e2m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Leon Bailey n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea quan t\u00e2m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/Leon-Bailey-noi-ve-tuong-lai-truoc-tin-don-duoc-Chelsea-quan-tam-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Bailey x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea quan t\u00e2m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1997 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn. Chelsea, Man City, Arsenal v\u00e0 Juventus \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 quan t\u00e2m ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Bayer Leverkusen. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00f2i 44 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/bailey-danh-tieng-voi-chelsea-va-arsenal-172-191957.html\" target=\"_blank\">Leon Bailey n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</span>, ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Bayer Leverkusen kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;\u0110\u00fang l\u00e0 Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb cho t\u00f4i, nh\u01b0ng nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng c\u00f2n t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n v\u00e0 Bayer Leverkusen. Hi\u1ec7n t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao nh\u1ea5t&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Leon Bailey mu\u1ed1n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Bundesliga c\u00f9ng Leverkusen</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Leverkusen thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. H\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 5 \u1edf Bundesliga v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 Champions League m\u00f9a t\u1edbi, Bayer Leverkusen k\u00e9m \u0111\u1ed9i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u Bayern Munich t\u1edbi 29 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"X\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea quan t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng hot Bundesliga h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"X\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea quan t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng hot Bundesliga h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/xac-nhan-arsenal-va-chelsea-quan-tam-leon-bailey.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Leon Bailey mu\u1ed1n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Bundesliga c\u00f9ng Leverkusen</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018 song Leon Bailey mu\u1ed1n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Bundesliga c\u00f9ng Leverkusen \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&quot;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Bundesliga m\u00f9a t\u1edbi. Bayern Munich l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong ba \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, h\u1ecd lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean s\u1ed1 1 cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch m\u1ed7i m\u00f9a. Tuy nhi\u00ean, n\u1ebfu c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i ch\u01a1i \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c trong t\u1eebng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c l\u1eadt \u0111\u1ed5 l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Bundesliga, Leverkusen hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu ch\u00fang t\u00f4i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 bi\u1ebfn \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2062","checkdouble":"193859"},{"date":"16:06 06/08","title":"U23 Th\u00e1i Lan lo\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i Myanmar","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/4/u23-thai-lan-loai-mot-loat-cau-thu-sau-that-bai-tai-myanmar.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u00e0n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu t\u1ea1i U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, HLV CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u00f4ng Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i cho m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>HLV\u00a0Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 U23 Oman trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1i 5/8 nh\u1edd b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi b\u1edfi h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a V\u0103n H\u1eadu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m b\u1edfi pha v\u1ea9y m\u00e1 ngo\u00e0i c\u1ee7a t\u00e0i n\u0103ng sinh n\u0103m 1999 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng xo\u00e1y l\u00ean cao r\u1ed3i cu\u1ed9n xu\u1ed1ng theo h\u00ecnh v\u00f2ng cung, r\u00f3t v\u00e0o g\u00f3c ch\u1ebft khung th\u00e0nh Oman.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam V\u0103n H\u1eadu l\u00e0 c\u1ee7a hi\u1ebfm c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam V\u0103n H\u1eadu l\u00e0 c\u1ee7a hi\u1ebfm c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/5/ly-do-u23-viet-nam-da-hai-tran-da-chinh-thuc-vo-dich.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a V\u0103n H\u1eadu</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn pha l\u00e0m b\u00e0n theo ki\u1ec3u Trivela n\u00e0y, v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t tr\u00ean Vnexpress: \u201c\u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu l\u00e0 h\u00e0ng hi\u1ebfm c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 c\u00e1i ch\u00e2n tr\u00e1i \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. Nh\u1edd v\u1eady, \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh trong kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn v\u00e0 ghi b\u00e0n\u201d.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng g\u1ed1c Th\u00e1i B\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. \u00d4ng Nghi\u00eam n\u00f3i th\u00eam: \"V\u0103n H\u1eadu c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn. Tuy nhi\u00ean, mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1eady c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ph\u1ea3i r\u00e8n luy\u1ec7n th\u00eam nhi\u1ec1u, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 t\u00ednh c\u00e1ch.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u0103n H\u1eadu c\u00f3 hai \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu. Th\u1ee9 nh\u1ea5t, v\u1eabn c\u00f2n l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb n\u00ean c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00f3ng v\u1ed9i trong x\u1eed l\u00fd. Th\u1ee9 hai, \u0111\u00f4i khi V\u0103n H\u1eadu n\u00f3ng t\u00ednh, v\u01b0\u1edbng v\u00e0o va ch\u1ea1m v\u00e0 tranh c\u00e3i kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft. \u0110i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh nh\u01b0 pha va ch\u1ea1m trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u00e0 \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng h\u00f4m 23/6. T\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean nh\u1eafc nh\u1edf c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f2n tr\u1ebb, c\u1ea7n t\u1eadp trung \u0111\u00e1 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 tr\u00e1nh tr\u1ea3 \u0111\u0169a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng\u201d.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u0103n H\u1eadu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 'c\u1ee7a hi\u1ebfm' c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. D\u00f9 m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 19 tu\u1ed5i song anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf kh\u1eafp c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i U19 cho t\u1edbi \u0110TQG. \u1ede c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 n\u00e0o th\u00ec V\u0103n H\u1eadu c\u0169ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft.</p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/5/Highlight-U23-Viet-Nam-vs-U23-Oman.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/u23-thai-lan-loai-mot-loat-cau-thu-sau-that-bai-tai-myanmar-168-193860.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/4/u23-thai-lan-loai-mot-loat-cau-thu-sau-that-bai-tai-myanmar.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/u23-thai-lan-loai-mot-loat-cau-thu-sau-that-bai-tai-myanmar-168-193860.html\">U23 Th\u00e1i Lan lo\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i Myanmar</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn thua t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu Alpine Cup 2018, ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n U23 Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh lo\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-olympic-indonesia-mat-ngoi-sao-sang-gia-nhat-tai-asiad-2018-168-193851.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2015/6/9/video-ban-thang-u23-indonesia-20-u23-philippines-vong-bang-seagame-28.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-olympic-indonesia-mat-ngoi-sao-sang-gia-nhat-tai-asiad-2018-168-193851.html\">\u0110T Olympic Indonesia m\u1ea5t ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018</span><br>\r\nTheo \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 ASIAD 2018 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao lai Ezra Walian v\u00ec l\u00fd do CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n RKC Waalwijk kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecbu nh\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2061","checkdouble":"193860"},{"date":"16:46 06/08","title":"Barca b\u00e1o tin bu\u1ed3n cho Arsenal v\u1ee5 \"bom t\u1ea5n\" 105 tri\u1ec7u euro","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/16/barca-bao-tin-buon-cho-arsenal-vu-dembele.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Arsenal mua Ousmane Dembele th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5p, Barca \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal quan t\u00e2m Dembele</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua Ousmane Dembele thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Barca, b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 105 tri\u1ec7u euro ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 19 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf La Liga. V\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn m\u00e0 Barca chi ra, nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n ch\u01b0a \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barca ch\u1eb7n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng Arsenal mua Ousmane Dembele  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Barca ch\u1eb7n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng Arsenal mua Ousmane Dembele  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/Barca-chan-duong-Arsenal-mua-Ousmane-Dembele--hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Ousmane Dembele</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Ousmane Dembele ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3, b\u1edfi Barca \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Malcom v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 42 tri\u1ec7u euro. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ef1u sao Dortmund \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch r\u1eddi Camp Nou \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018. Hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1997.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/arsenal-co-co-hoi-so-huu-bom-tan-cua-barca-172-192623.html\" target=\"_blank\">Arsenal mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Ousmane Dembele</span>, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a, n\u1ebfu ng\u00f4i sao 21 tu\u1ed5i ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London s\u1ebd mua \u0111\u1ee9t v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 85 tri\u1ec7u euro. Chelsea c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 quan t\u00e2m ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Barca.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ousmane Dembele kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi Barca</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Arsenal mua Ousmane Dembele th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5p, Barca \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ousmane Dembele co the roi Camp Nou neu Barca mua Willian\" title=\"Ousmane Dembele c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Camp Nou n\u1ebfu Barca mua Willian\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/Giam-doc-the-thao-Barca-chot-tuong-lai-Dembele-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Ousmane Dembele\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb RAC1 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Josep Maria Bartomeu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1997 \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, HLV Ernesto Valverde c\u0169ng\u00a0mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u1edf l\u1ea1i. Barca tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Dembele v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 gi\u00e1 n\u00e0o.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1eadm ch\u00ed t\u1edd b\u00e1o c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u00f2n kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Barca coi Ousmane Dembele l\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Malcom, Coutinho, Arthur, Clement Lenglet v\u00e0 Umtiti l\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Barca trong nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Dembele \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1997 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: \u201cM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua t\u00f4i d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u, nh\u01b0ng l\u00fac n\u00e0y t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2060","checkdouble":"193861"},{"date":"16:38 06/08","title":"Jurgen Klopp kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch cho Liverpool m\u00f9a t\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/jurgen-klopp-khong-dat-muc-tieu-vo-dich-cho-liverpool-mua-toi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u00f9 chi c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed1ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ed5 sung l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0ng Jurgen Klopp kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch cho Liverpool trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018-19 \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh g\u00e2y \u00e1p l\u1ef1c cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2.</h2><h2>Jurgen Klopp kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 chi ra h\u01a1n 160 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ed5 sung l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi 4 c\u00e1i t\u00ean g\u1ed3m Alisson Becker, Fabinho, Naby Keita v\u00e0 Xherdan Shaqiri. The Kop c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng n\u00e0o ngo\u00e0i Emre Can, v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 sung b\u1eb1ng hai c\u00e1i t\u00ean l\u00e0 Keita v\u00e0 Fabinho.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jurgen Klopp khong dat muc tieu vo dich cho Liverpool mua toi.\" title=\"Jurgen Klopp kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch cho Liverpool m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/jurgen-klopp-khong-dat-muc-tieu-vo-dich-cho-liverpool-mua-toi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Jurgen Klopp kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch cho Liverpool m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 v\u1eady, HLV Jurgen Klopp kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i ch\u01b0a b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u: &quot;Gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u lu\u00f4n r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 ng\u1ed3i \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, r\u1ed3i t\u1ef1 s\u01b0\u1edbng b\u1eb1ng c\u00e2u n\u00f3i '\u1ed3, m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ea5y'.&quot;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng trong t\u1eebng tu\u1ea7n, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 v\u00e0i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>T\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Liverpool s\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi khi g\u1eb7p West Ham tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. H\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 v\u1ed1n ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u0111ang b\u1ecb lo ng\u1ea1i khi m\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t c\u00e1i t\u00ean v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Joel Matip ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00f4ng, c\u00f2n Ragnar Klavan d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u00e2n kheo. C\u1ea3 hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Napoli \u1edf tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t. Ngo\u00e0i ra, Dejan Lovren \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Klopp x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng ra s\u00e2n \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p West Ham do th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lovren v\u1eabn \u0111ang trong k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 h\u1eadu World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 Klopp cho bi\u1ebft c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u1ea7n th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u. Trung v\u1ec7 ngo\u00e0i Croatia \u00edt nh\u1ea5t b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Liverpool m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018-19:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-co-the-no-them-bom-tan-cho-liverpool-172-193799.html\">Klopp h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n n\u1ed5 th\u00eam bom t\u1ea5n &ldquo;ph\u00fat 89&rdquo; cho Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/huyen-thoai-liverpool-dat-dau-hoi-ve-tan-binh-alisson-172-193787.html\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i nghi ng\u1edd kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng bom t\u1ea5n c\u1ee7a Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/ancelotti-bo-hop-bao-sau-tham-bai-truoc-liverpool-176-193747.html\">Ancelotti b\u1ecf h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-liverpool-50-napoli-giao-huu-clb-he-2018-329-193740.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Liverpool 5-0 Napoli (Giao h\u1eefu CLB h\u00e8 2018)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/robbie-fowler-nhan-xet-liverpool-mua-toi-se-rat-dang-so-172-193729.html\">V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, Liverpool m\u00f9a t\u1edbi s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/liverpool-vs-napoli-giao-huu-clb-he-2018-372-193724.html\">Liverpool 5-0 Napoli: The Klopp h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t \u00e1 qu\u00e2n Serie A trong ng\u00e0y Alisson ra m\u1eaft</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2059","checkdouble":"193862"},{"date":"16:30 06/08","title":"\"V\u0103n H\u1eadu l\u00e0 c\u1ee7a hi\u1ebfm c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/van-hau-la-cua-hiem-cua-bong-da-viet.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u00e0n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu t\u1ea1i U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, HLV CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u00f4ng Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i cho m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>HLV\u00a0Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 U23 Oman trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1i 5/8 nh\u1edd b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi b\u1edfi h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a V\u0103n H\u1eadu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m b\u1edfi pha v\u1ea9y m\u00e1 ngo\u00e0i c\u1ee7a t\u00e0i n\u0103ng sinh n\u0103m 1999 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng xo\u00e1y l\u00ean cao r\u1ed3i cu\u1ed9n xu\u1ed1ng theo h\u00ecnh v\u00f2ng cung, r\u00f3t v\u00e0o g\u00f3c ch\u1ebft khung th\u00e0nh Oman.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam V\u0103n H\u1eadu l\u00e0 c\u1ee7a hi\u1ebfm c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam V\u0103n H\u1eadu l\u00e0 c\u1ee7a hi\u1ebfm c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/5/ly-do-u23-viet-nam-da-hai-tran-da-chinh-thuc-vo-dich.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a V\u0103n H\u1eadu</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn pha l\u00e0m b\u00e0n theo ki\u1ec3u Trivela n\u00e0y, v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t tr\u00ean Vnexpress: \u201c\u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu l\u00e0 h\u00e0ng hi\u1ebfm c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 c\u00e1i ch\u00e2n tr\u00e1i \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. Nh\u1edd v\u1eady, \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh trong kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn v\u00e0 ghi b\u00e0n\u201d.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng g\u1ed1c Th\u00e1i B\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. \u00d4ng Nghi\u00eam n\u00f3i th\u00eam: \"V\u0103n H\u1eadu c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn. Tuy nhi\u00ean, mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1eady c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ph\u1ea3i r\u00e8n luy\u1ec7n th\u00eam nhi\u1ec1u, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 t\u00ednh c\u00e1ch.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u0103n H\u1eadu c\u00f3 hai \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu. Th\u1ee9 nh\u1ea5t, v\u1eabn c\u00f2n l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb n\u00ean c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00f3ng v\u1ed9i trong x\u1eed l\u00fd. Th\u1ee9 hai, \u0111\u00f4i khi V\u0103n H\u1eadu n\u00f3ng t\u00ednh, v\u01b0\u1edbng v\u00e0o va ch\u1ea1m v\u00e0 tranh c\u00e3i kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft. \u0110i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh nh\u01b0 pha va ch\u1ea1m trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u00e0 \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng h\u00f4m 23/6. T\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean nh\u1eafc nh\u1edf c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f2n tr\u1ebb, c\u1ea7n t\u1eadp trung \u0111\u00e1 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 tr\u00e1nh tr\u1ea3 \u0111\u0169a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng\u201d.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u0103n H\u1eadu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 'c\u1ee7a hi\u1ebfm' c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. D\u00f9 m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 19 tu\u1ed5i song anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf kh\u1eafp c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i U19 cho t\u1edbi \u0110TQG. \u1ede c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 n\u00e0o th\u00ec V\u0103n H\u1eadu c\u0169ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft.</p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/5/Highlight-U23-Viet-Nam-vs-U23-Oman.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/u23-thai-lan-loai-mot-loat-cau-thu-sau-that-bai-tai-myanmar-168-193860.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/4/u23-thai-lan-loai-mot-loat-cau-thu-sau-that-bai-tai-myanmar.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/u23-thai-lan-loai-mot-loat-cau-thu-sau-that-bai-tai-myanmar-168-193860.html\">U23 Th\u00e1i Lan lo\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i Myanmar</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn thua t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu Alpine Cup 2018, ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n U23 Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh lo\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-olympic-indonesia-mat-ngoi-sao-sang-gia-nhat-tai-asiad-2018-168-193851.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2015/6/9/video-ban-thang-u23-indonesia-20-u23-philippines-vong-bang-seagame-28.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-olympic-indonesia-mat-ngoi-sao-sang-gia-nhat-tai-asiad-2018-168-193851.html\">\u0110T Olympic Indonesia m\u1ea5t ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018</span><br>\r\nTheo \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 ASIAD 2018 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao lai Ezra Walian v\u00ec l\u00fd do CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n RKC Waalwijk kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecbu nh\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2058","checkdouble":"193864"},{"date":"16:51 06/08","title":"Leroy San\u00e9: Gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng t\u01b0 t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ec3 \u201c\u0111\u00e1 nh\u01b0 Messi\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/leroy-sane-giai-phong-tu-tuong-de-da-nhu-messi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u1eddi d\u1ea1y ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0: \u201cH\u00e3y \u0111\u00e1 nh\u01b0 Messi.\u201d Hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean Pep Guardiola c\u1ee7a Manchester City n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Leroy San\u00e9 sau khi k\u1ebft th\u00fac bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y m\u00f9a thu n\u0103m 2016. </h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Kh\u00e1 l\u00e2u tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi danh s\u00e1ch tham d\u1ef1 v\u00f2ng chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c, Leroy San\u00e9 t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean Pep Guardiola n\u00f3i &ldquo;h\u00e3y \u0111\u00e1 nh\u01b0 Messi.&rdquo; Sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a h\u00e8 d\u00e0i ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea7y \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i.</strong><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Leroy Sane: Giai phong tu tuong de da nhu Messi\" title=\"Leroy San\u00e9: Gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng t\u01b0 t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 nh\u01b0 Messi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/GettyImages-8613351961.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Leroy San\u00e9: Gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng t\u01b0 t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 nh\u01b0 Messi</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u1eddi d\u1ea1y ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0: &ldquo;H\u00e3y \u0111\u00e1 nh\u01b0 Messi.&rdquo; Hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean Pep Guardiola c\u1ee7a Manchester City n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Leroy San\u00e9 sau khi k\u1ebft th\u00fac bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y m\u00f9a thu n\u0103m 2016. San\u00e9, ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1edbn l\u00ean v\u1edbi ni\u1ec1m c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng t\u1eeb si\u00eau sao Argentina (c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Cristiano Ronaldo) \u1edf Wattenscheid, v\u00f9ng ngo\u1ea1i \u00f4 th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Bochum, \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1p l\u1ea1i l\u1eddi c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t n\u1ee5 c\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea7y ho\u00e0i nghi. &ldquo;Ch\u1eb3ng ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 Messi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3,&rdquo; anh ph\u1ea3n ph\u00e1o. &ldquo;Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 duy nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t Messi th\u00f4i.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Catalonia \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u00ecnh v\u1edbi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0ng Guardiola c\u0169ng b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch r\u1eb1ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 22 tu\u1ed5i n\u00ean h\u1ecdc theo t\u01b0 duy ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng t\u1ea1i Barcelona, ph\u1ea3i th\u1ea5y &ldquo;t\u1ef1 do&rdquo; v\u00e0 &ldquo;vui&rdquo; v\u1edbi tr\u00e1i b\u00f3ng. San\u00e9 hi\u1ec3u \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. C\u00e1c bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia ph\u00e2n t\u00edch video v\u00e0 c\u00e1c b\u00e0i t\u1eadp chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt v\u1edbi c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed9 cao \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng di chuy\u1ec3n c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ch\u1ecdn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u00fap anh khai ph\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n n\u1eefa kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, anh ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 mong mu\u1ed1n n\u1ebfu t\u00e2m l\u00fd c\u0169ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i. \u00c1p l\u1ef1c ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t trong 1/3 s\u00e2n \u1edf b\u00ean \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1eebng khi\u1ebfn anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 h\u01a1n n\u1eefa \u1edf Schalke 04, ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho s\u1ef1 &ldquo;an nhi\u00ean&rdquo; &ndash; m\u1ed9t c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c \u0111\u1eafm ch\u00ecm trong ni\u1ec1m vui v\u00f4 b\u1edd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng b\u1eadc th\u1ea7y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.&nbsp; M\u1ea5u ch\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ti\u1ebfn l\u00ean, nh\u01b0 Guardiola gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch, l\u00e0 c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i bu\u00f4ng b\u1ecf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sane\" title=\"Sane\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/Diem-tin-bong-da-sang-247-Ai-la-doi-thu-lon-nhat-cua-Man-City-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Sane</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Th\u1eadt kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 khi chuy\u1ec3n t\u1eeb Bundesliga t\u1edbi Premier League,&rdquo; San\u00e9 chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi tu\u1ea7n b\u00e1o Welt am Sonntag h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m nay. &ldquo;Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Anh nhanh v\u00e0 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd h\u01a1n. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t kinh ng\u1ea1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn, nh\u1eefng t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i l\u1edbn v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef m\u1edbi.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t v\u00e0i th\u00e1ng sau khi anh chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Manchester City, c\u00f3 v\u1ebb nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng nghi ng\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00fang. D\u00f9 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd r\u1eb1ng San\u00e9 &ndash; con trai c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng Souleymane San\u00e9 (c\u1ef1u tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Senegal v\u00e0 l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng \u1edf Bundesliga trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o SG Wattenscheid 09 v\u00e0 SC Freiburg) v\u00e0 b\u00e0 Regina Weber-San\u00e9 (ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n t\u1ea5m huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1ec3 d\u1ee5c nh\u1ecbp \u0111i\u1ec7u cho \u0111o\u00e0n T\u00e2y \u0110\u1ee9c \u1edf Olympic 1984 t\u1ea1i Los Angeles) &ndash; h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee7 m\u1ecdi ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u01b0ng th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m anh t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad \u0111\u00e3 v\u1ea5p ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch. Manchester City \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i chi ra 50 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a San\u00e9 nh\u01b0ng khi \u0111\u00f3 \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 20, anh b\u1ecb xem l\u00e0 c\u00f2n qu\u00e1 thi\u1ebfu kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng Premier League.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;M\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ea7n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh xem li\u1ec7u anh ta mu\u1ed1n s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh g\u1eafn li\u1ec1n v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n b\u1ea1c hay c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh t\u1ef1u th\u1ec3 thao,&rdquo; Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh Bayern Munich, Karl-Heinz Rummenigge n\u00f3i. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u0110\u1ee9c c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 San\u00e9 v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1ebfu Guardiola kh\u00f4ng chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Etihad c\u00f9ng n\u0103m \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pep Guardiola\" title=\"Pep Guardiola\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/HLV-Pep-Guardiola-khen-ngoi-Sergio-Aguero-va-Bernardo-Silva-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Pep Guardiola v\u00e0 danh hi\u1ec7u th\u1ee9 2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf Anh</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Ngay khi Pep g\u1ecdi \u0111i\u1ec7n cho t\u00f4i v\u00e0 n\u00f3i \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n t\u00f4i gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh mu\u1ed1n thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho \u00f4ng \u1ea5y,&rdquo; San\u00e9 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf. &ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Bayern Munich c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng [khi c\u00f2n \u1edf Schalke] v\u00e0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5y c\u00e1ch h\u1ecd ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng. Th\u1eadt \u0111\u00e1ng kinh ng\u1ea1c; r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n m\u1ed7i khi ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi h\u1ecd.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean khi anh kho\u00e1c \u00e1o The Citizens kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. Guardiola kh\u00f4ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng anh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Catalonia mu\u1ed1n c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng anh c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng. May m\u1eafn l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 thi\u1ebfu b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh n\u00e0o c\u1ea3. &ldquo;\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean r\u1ea5t ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn v\u1edbi t\u00f4i,&rdquo; San\u00e9 nh\u1edb l\u1ea1i. &ldquo;H\u1ecd n\u00f3i, &lsquo;H\u00e3y tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n, Leroy!&rsquo; Gi\u1edd th\u00ec \u0111\u1ea7u t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 tr\u00fat b\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00e1nh n\u1eb7ng trong \u0111\u1ea7u.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi t\u01b0 t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng, nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c pha ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o c\u0169ng t\u1edbi. S\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh, nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ea1y th\u1ea7n t\u1ed1c, nh\u1eefng pha x\u1eed l\u00fd b\u00f3ng kh\u00e9o l\u00e9o v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng quan s\u00e1t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i si\u00eau vi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a San\u00e9 l\u00e0 c\u00e1c nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 ch\u00ednh gi\u00fap Manchester City v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y. Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng v\u1eady, c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia c\u00f2n cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Pep Guardiola ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t th\u1ee9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 &ldquo;hay nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1edbi nay&rdquo;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sane Man City\" title=\"Sane Man City\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/5/David-Villa-du-doan-Man-City-thong-tri-Premier-League-mua-toi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Sane&nbsp; l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh c\u00f9ng Man City</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;C\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u1eadt \u0111\u00e1ng kinh ng\u1ea1c. Leroy c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi,&rdquo; Guardiola chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi The Guardian. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 th\u1ebf, \u00f4ng c\u00f2n so s\u00e1nh s\u1ee9c h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c trong kh\u00f4ng gian h\u1eb9p c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u00e0 &ldquo;ai c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft l\u00e0 ai&rdquo;. &ldquo;V\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch l\u00e0 hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean c\u0169 c\u1ee7a Messi, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u1ecfi h\u01a1n n\u1eefa. M\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf, th\u1eadt \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 ai \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn ra ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Guardiola n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi lu\u00f4n ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eebng chi ti\u1ebft d\u00f9 nh\u1ecf nh\u1ea5t, v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap \u00f4ng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u trong c\u00f4ng cu\u1ed9c bi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111a n\u0103ng Leroy San\u00e9 th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao. &ldquo;\u00d4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea7u t\u00f4i \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y,&rdquo; San\u00e9 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf. &ldquo;C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u00e0 to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i &ndash; c\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u, c\u00e1ch t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i di chuy\u1ec3n v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u00f3ng hay khi c\u00f3 b\u00f3ng. C\u00e1ch \u00f4ng \u1ea5y gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 th\u1eadt \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng &ndash; \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y t\u1ed1t cho c\u1ea3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1eabn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi Raheem Sterling g\u1ecdi San\u00e9 l\u00e0 &ldquo;Harry Potter c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c&rdquo; tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Anh ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n tr\u00eau ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00ec b\u1ed9 qu\u1ea7n \u00e1o nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed3ng ph\u1ee5c h\u1ecdc sinh trong m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i ch\u1ee5p h\u00ecnh th\u1eddi trang. Tuy nhi\u00ean, n\u1ebfu x\u00e9t \u1edf m\u1ed9t kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh kh\u00e1c th\u00ec c\u00e1i bi\u1ec7t danh \u1ea5y c\u0169ng kh\u00e1 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Schalke 04: V\u1edbi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng thi\u00ean b\u1ea9m, San\u00e9 \u0111ang d\u1ea7n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u1ea7y ph\u1ee7 th\u1ee7y gi\u1ecfi nh\u1ea5t \u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Guardiola.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sane va Low\" title=\"Sane v\u00e0 Low\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/22/sane-khong-trach-low-vi-quyet-dinh-o-nha-xem-world-cup.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Sane v\u00e0 Low</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ecf qua vi\u1ec7c lo\u1ea1i Leroy San\u00e9 ra kh\u1ecfi danh s\u00e1ch tham d\u1ef1 World Cup, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean Joachim L\u00f6w c\u0169ng b\u1ecb m\u00ea ho\u1eb7c b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ea1y v\u00e0 c\u00e1c pha x\u1eed l\u00fd nh\u01b0 th\u00f4i mi\u00ean c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Manchester City. &ldquo;C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 m\u01b0u m\u1eb9o v\u00e0 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t: t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng di chuy\u1ec3n th\u00f4ng minh,&rdquo; L\u00f6w n\u00f3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m Euro 2016. S\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 nh\u01b0 v\u0169 b\u00e3o k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn anh su\u00fdt ch\u00fat n\u1eefa tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed1i \u0111e d\u1ecda thay th\u1ebf nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m h\u01a1n t\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga m\u00f9a h\u00e8 v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng tr\u1ebb tri\u1ec3n v\u1ecdng m\u00e0 L\u00f6w c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn, kh\u00f4ng ai thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cao nh\u01b0 San\u00e9 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Manchester City m\u00f9a h\u00e8 v\u1eeba qua. V\u00e0 ngo\u00e0i San\u00e9 ra, c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ea1y l\u1eaft l\u00e9o xuy\u00ean ph\u00e1 h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc xe Tron Light Cycle.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2014, L\u00f6w t\u1eebng n\u00f3i m\u1ed9t c\u00e2u n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi Mario G\u00f6tze tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tung c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u00e0o s\u00e2n: &ldquo;h\u00e3y cho th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi th\u1ea5y c\u1eadu gi\u1ecfi h\u01a1n Messi.&rdquo; Nh\u01b0ng 4 n\u0103m sau, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00f3i v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 &ldquo;h\u00e3y \u0111\u00e1 nh\u01b0 Messi&rdquo; gi\u1ed1ng Pep Guardiola khi Die Mannschaft g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed5i th\u00e0nh &ldquo;h\u00e3y \u0111\u00e1 nh\u01b0 San\u00e9&rdquo; c\u00f3 l\u1ebd ma thu\u1eadt c\u0169ng s\u1ebd xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n tr\u00ean s\u00e2n th\u00f4i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em><strong>D\u1ecbch t\u1eeb b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft &ldquo;Free your mind&rdquo; c\u1ee7a t\u00e1c gi\u1ea3 Raphael Honigstein tr\u00ean Eight By Eight.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</strong></em><strong><em>CG</em>&nbsp;(TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2057","checkdouble":"193865"},{"date":"17:18 06/08","title":"Thi\u1ebfu Ronaldo, Real v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/kroos-phat-bieu-ve-real-khi-khong-co-ronaldo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Toni Kroos ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Real khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 Ronaldo. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ronaldo r\u1eddi Real t\u1edbi Juventus</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf chung k\u1ebft Champions League v\u1edbi Liverpool m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c v\u1edbi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u g\u1ee3i m\u1edf v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c chia tay v\u1edbi Real Madrid. Kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u sau, anh k\u00fd v\u00e0o h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Juventus. \u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Ronaldo, \u0111\u1ea1i gia Italia ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 cho Real s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea7m quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Ronaldo v\u1edbi Real l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i b\u00e0n c\u00e3i. 9 m\u00f9a tr\u00f4i qua, CR7 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 450 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 438 tr\u1eadn, v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u danh s\u00e1ch l\u00e0m b\u00e0n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Toni Kroos ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Real khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 Ronaldo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Toni Kroos ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Real khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 Ronaldo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/kroos-phat-bieu-ve-real-khi-khong-co-ronaldo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Kroos ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Real khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 Ronaldo \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ef1 tin</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ed1ng k\u00ea ch\u1ec9 ra c\u1ee9 84,05 ph\u00fat, Ronaldo l\u1ea1i ghi 1 b\u00e0n cho Real. Ngo\u00e0i 450 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, anh c\u0169ng c\u00f3 119 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o cho \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Real v\u1eabn b\u1ea5t kh\u1ea3 chi\u1ebfn b\u1ea1i</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">5 n\u0103m qua, Real Madrid gi\u00e0nh t\u1edbi 4 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League v\u00e0 1 La Liga ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 c\u00e1c danh hi\u1ec7u nh\u1ecf h\u01a1n. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, Toni Kroos ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Real khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 Ronaldo \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ef1 tin. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i tin r\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf CR7 song Los Blancos kh\u00f4ng v\u00ec th\u1ebf m\u00e0 l\u1ee5i b\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c50 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Ronaldo l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 thay th\u1ebf\u201d, Kroos n\u00f3i v\u1edbi t\u1edd Kicker. \u201cAnh \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 m\u1eaft x\u00edch quan tr\u1ecdng trong \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i trong v\u00e0i n\u0103m qua v\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh trong s\u1ef1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. Nh\u01b0ng Real v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0<br>\r\nT\u1edbi l\u00fac n\u00e0y, Real v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn thay cho Ronaldo. H\u1ecd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u00f3n v\u1ec1 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Vinicius Junior m\u1edbi 18 tu\u1ed5i sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1ea1i Flamengo.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/lucas-vazquez-muon-real-giu-chan-bang-duoc-cai-ten-nay-172-193838.html\">Lucas Vazquez mu\u1ed1n Real gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u00e0y?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-sap-bien-harry-kane-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi-180-193833.html\">Real Madrid s\u1eafp bi\u1ebfn Harry Kane \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/willian-mot-lan-nua-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-172-193826.html\">Willian: T\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 r\u1eddi Chelsea \u0111\u1ebfn MU ho\u1eb7c Real n\u1ebfu...</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-nham-muc-tieu-200-trieu-euro-thay-modric-180-193772.html\">Real Madrid nh\u1eafm m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau 200 tri\u1ec7u euro thay Modric</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/hlv-juventus-real-van-rat-dang-so-du-khong-co-ronaldo-180-193768.html\">HLV Juventus: Real v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2056","checkdouble":"193866"},{"date":"17:43 06/08","title":"HLV Ph\u1ea1m Minh \u0110\u1ee9c k\u1ec3 c\u00f4ng m\u00e0i d\u0169a \"ng\u1ecdc th\u00f4\" \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/hlv-pham-minh-duc-ke-cong-mai-giua-ngoc-tho-doan-van-hau.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, v\u1ecb HLV \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, \u00f4ng Ph\u1ea1m Minh \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafc l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng m\u1ed1c th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, khi \u00f4ng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu.</h2><h2>HLV Ph\u1ea1m Minh \u0110\u1ee9c k\u1ec3 c\u00f4ng m\u00e0i gi\u0169a \"ng\u1ecdc th\u00f4\" \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu\u00a0</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-oman-19h30-toi-ngay-hom-nay-58-372-193775.html\" target=\"_blank\">U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman</span> t\u1ed1i qua 5/8, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 pha ghi b\u00e0n \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169, HLV Ph\u1ea1m Minh \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n b\u1edfi \u00f4ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Ph\u1ea1m Minh \u0110\u1ee9c k\u1ec3 c\u00f4ng m\u00e0i gi\u0169a ng\u1ecdc th\u00f4 \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Ph\u1ea1m Minh \u0110\u1ee9c k\u1ec3 c\u00f4ng m\u00e0i gi\u0169a ng\u1ecdc th\u00f4 \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/tong-hop-nhung-ban-thang-dep-mat-cua-doan-van-hau.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Ph\u1ea1m Minh \u0110\u1ee9c d\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ee3i ng\u1ee3i khen cho h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb n\u00e0y n\u00f3i tr\u00ean MASK Online: \u201cTrong l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1999, V\u0103n H\u1eadu lu\u00f4n lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng nh\u1ea5t. L\u00fac \u0111\u00f3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111ang ch\u01a1i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i th\u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 n\u00e0o c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi \u0111\u00e0n anh nh\u01b0 Quang H\u1ea3i, \u0110\u1eadu V\u0103n To\u00e0n\u2026 n\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a V\u0103n H\u1eadu v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00e1 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00f4i c\u0169ng n\u00f3i v\u1edbi V\u0103n H\u1eadu r\u1eb1ng n\u1ebfu v\u1ec1 ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7, ch\u1ec9 1 n\u0103m th\u00f4i l\u00e0 H\u1eadu s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00ean ch\u01a1i V-League, b\u1edfi l\u00fac \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111ang thi\u1ebfu ng\u01b0\u1eddi. V\u0103n H\u1eadu c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh r\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eb9p, s\u1edf h\u1eefu chi\u1ec1u cao t\u1ed1t, ch\u00e2n tr\u00e1i r\u1ea5t kh\u00e9o, l\u1ea1i m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd v\u00e0 c\u00f3 s\u1ee9c b\u1eadt t\u1ed1t. Ngo\u00e0i ra, V\u0103n H\u1eadu c\u00f2n c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u pha \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n r\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eb9p r\u1ed3i b\u1eadt cao \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ef1c hay.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1edbi pha ghi b\u00e0n h\u00f4m qua. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf h\u1ecd c\u00f3 li\u1ec1u th\u00ec c\u0169ng l\u00e0 b\u1edfi h\u1ecd c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng. V\u0103n H\u1eadu xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7, n\u00ean khi l\u00ean t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng khu v\u1ef1c \u0111\u00f3 em \u1ea5y th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean s\u00fat xa\".</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Video: T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft c\u1ee7a \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu<span style=\"white-space: pre;\">\t</span></strong></p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/6/20180805_06_van_hau_compilatio.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height: 220px;\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c ng\u1ee3i khen c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169, HLV Ph\u1ea1m Minh \u0110\u1ee9c c\u0169ng hy v\u1ecdng trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu. C\u00f3 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap n\u00e2ng t\u1ea7m n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 v\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc nhanh h\u01a1n t\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau World Cup.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb n\u00e0y n\u00f3i th\u00eam: \"N\u00f3i chung, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 V\u0103n H\u1eadu. Tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u00fang ta gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean t\u1ea7m ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c r\u1ed3i. Thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng T\u00e2y \u00c1 nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. Ph\u00fat 89 r\u1ed3i m\u00e0 v\u1eabn d\u1eabn b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00ean t\u1edbi v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1ed3i tung ra pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m r\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mong r\u1eb1ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng trung t\u00e2m nh\u01b0 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, HAGL, PVF, Viettel, SLNA, nh\u1eefng n\u01a1i \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 cho U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u01b0 b\u00e2y gi\u1edd, \u0111\u1ec3 qua \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 th\u00eam nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn. Khi \u1ea5y gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 World Cup c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta c\u0169ng s\u1ebd s\u1edbm tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c\".<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\n</strong></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/van-hau-la-cua-hiem-cua-bong-da-viet-168-193864.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/van-hau-la-cua-hiem-cua-bong-da-viet.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/van-hau-la-cua-hiem-cua-bong-da-viet-168-193864.html\">V\u0103n H\u1eadu l\u00e0 c\u1ee7a hi\u1ebfm c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t</span><br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u00e0n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu t\u1ea1i U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, HLV CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u00f4ng Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i cho m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hiem-cau-thu-vleague-nao-lam-duoc-nhu-doan-van-hau-168-193801.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/hiem-cau-thu-vleague-nao-lam-duoc-nhu-doan-van-hau.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hiem-cau-thu-vleague-nao-lam-duoc-nhu-doan-van-hau-168-193801.html\">\u201cHi\u1ebfm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 V-League n\u00e0o l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0 \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu\u201d</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Oman, Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch H\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3ng HLV qu\u1ed1c gia, \u00f4ng Nguy\u1ec5n S\u1ef9 Hi\u1ec3n cho r\u1eb1ng pha l\u00e0m b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 r\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eb7c...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-khen-ngoi-2-cai-ten-xuat-sac-sau-tran-thang-oman-168-193795.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/hlv-park-hang-seo-khen-ngoi-2-cai-ten-xuat-sac-sau-tran-thang-oman.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-khen-ngoi-2-cai-ten-xuat-sac-sau-tran-thang-oman-168-193795.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo khen ng\u1ee3i 2 c\u00e1i t\u00ean xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Oman</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh l\u1eddi khen cho hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng v\u00e0 \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2055","checkdouble":"193868"},{"date":"17:50 06/08","title":"4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i khi Arturo Vidal t\u1edbi Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/6/4-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-khi-arturo-vidal-toi-barca.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Arturo Vidal t\u1edbi Barca v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 20 tri\u1ec7u euro t\u1eeb Bayern Munich, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua danh s\u00e1ch 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i khi Arturo Vidal t\u1edbi Barca.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Ernesto Valverde</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Ernesto Valverde \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea5t 2 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, theo \u0111\u00f3 Andres Iniesta r\u1eddi Barca sau 22 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3, anh c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Vissel Kobe c\u1ee7a Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. Paulinho c\u0169ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Qu\u1ea3ng Ch\u00e2u H\u1eb1ng \u0110\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i khi Arturo Vidal t\u1edbi Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i khi Arturo Vidal t\u1edbi Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/4-nguoi-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-khi-Arturo-Vidal-toi-Barca-hinh-anh.jpg\"><br>\r\n            &nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ernesto Valverde r\u1ea5t vui khi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Vidal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nPaulinho v\u00e0 Iniesta l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean c\u1ee7a Valverde \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecd ra \u0111i b\u1ecf l\u1ea1i kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa. Arthur \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u01b0ng n\u0103m nay anh m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 21 tu\u1ed5i, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn cho t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u00e0 c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m, sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/barca-chinh-thuc-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-sao-khung-bayern-munich-180-193675.html\" target=\"_blank\">Barca mua Arturo Vidal th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng</span>. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, anh kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 c\u00f2n s\u1edf h\u1eefu kinh nghi\u1ec7m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi Vidal, \u00f4ng Valverde \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c vui s\u01b0\u1edbng c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u HLV Bilbao: &ldquo;Vidal l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi mang l\u1ea1i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho Barca \u1edf h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Inter Milan</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi Arturo Vidal kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chia tay Bayern Munich \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c Inter Milan nh\u1ea3y v\u00e0o \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n. H\u1ecd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile s\u1edbm nh\u1ea5t, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milan r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Vidal tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Serie A.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Inter lo co hoi chieu mo Vidal\" title=\"Inter l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Vidal\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/inter.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Inter l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Vidal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Bild, Inter mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n Vidal m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi mua \u0111\u1ee9t v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 25 tri\u1ec7u euro, song Bayern \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ee9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1987, khi Inter c\u00f2n \u0111ang suy ngh\u0129 th\u00ec h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea5t Vidal v\u00e0o tay Barca.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i, Inter \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 vi\u1ec7c k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd h\u1ecd n\u00ean t\u1ef1 tr\u00e1ch m\u00ecnh v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng quy\u1ebft \u0111o\u00e1n trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Vidal, Inter \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang Luka Modric c\u1ee7a Real Madrid, song ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Florentino Perez \u0111\u00f2i \u0111\u1ebfn 750 tri\u1ec7u euro cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Arturo Vidal</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arturo Vidal tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Bayern Munich \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p, ng\u00f4i sao 31 tu\u1ed5i \u01b0u ti\u00ean c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Vidal co co hoi cung Barca gianh nhung danh hieu lon\" title=\"Vidal c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u00f9ng Barca gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/vidal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Vidal c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u00f9ng Barca gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nInter Milan \u0111ang cho th\u1ea5y quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn, song h\u1ecd v\u1eabn b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n so v\u1edbi Juventus. N\u1ebfu c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milan, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Vidal c\u00f9ng Inter v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Serie A m\u00f9a t\u1edbi l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1edbi Barca, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Vidal c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn l\u00e0 cao h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n Real trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua t\u1edbi danh hi\u1ec7u La Liga m\u00f9a t\u1edbi, b\u1edfi trong khi Barca \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh th\u00ec Los Blancos kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u1edbn, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n suy y\u1ebfu khi m\u1ea5t Ronaldo.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Camp Nou, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Vidal c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh c\u0169ng cao h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n \u1edf Inter Milan. Trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Barca m\u00f9a t\u1edbi, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ef1u sao Juventus s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 thay v\u1ecb tr\u00ed do Paulinho \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Italia kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Inter Milan, s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Radja Nainggolan, Joao Mario, Marcelo Brozovic v\u00e0 Matias Vecino c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1987 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Denis Suarez</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua Denis Suarez ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh c\u00f3 4 l\u1ea7n \u1edf La Liga, vi\u1ec7c s\u1edf h\u1eefu qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m khi\u1ebfn HLV Ernesto Valverde r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Denis Suarez kho canh tranh vi tri voi Vidal\" title=\"Denis Suarez kh\u00f3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi Vidal\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/suarez.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Denis Suarez kh\u00f3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi Vidal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng Andres Iniesta, Ivan Rakitic, Sergio Busquets, Paulinho v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Philippe Coutinho n\u1eefa, s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh. \u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng hy v\u1ecdng cho Denis Suarez khi Paulinho v\u00e0 Iniesta ra \u0111i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, hy v\u1ecdng v\u1eeba m\u1edf ra \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3ng l\u1ea1i b\u1edfi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Arturo Vidal.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n binh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Denis Suarez l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5p. Bi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nR\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, HLV Valverde kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 c\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 24 tu\u1ed5i, b\u1edfi v\u1eady \u0111\u1ec3 anh ra \u0111i theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u00f3 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Leon Goretzka</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi Denis Suarez \u1edf Barca th\u00ec c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1ea1i m\u1edf ra v\u1edbi Leon Goretzka \u1edf Bayern Munich.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Leon Goretzka se co co hoi duoc ra san nhieu hon khi Vidal ra di\" title=\"Leon Goretzka s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n khi Vidal ra \u0111i\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/gotze.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Leon Goretzka s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n khi Vidal ra \u0111i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao 22 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eeba ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Bayern Munich t\u1eeb Schalke, trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o &ldquo;H\u00f9m x\u00e1m&rdquo; Vidal s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a Goretzka trong vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi t\u00e2n HLV Niko Kovac.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Barca, ng\u00f4i sao 22 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n m\u00ecnh h\u01a1n.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGoretzka \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Barca \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1edbi Bayern, sau khi Vidal ra \u0111i, gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ec1u cho r\u1eb1ng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i \u0110KV\u0110 Bundesliga c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t s\u00e1ng su\u1ed1t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Rafinha v\u00e0 Thiago Alcantara</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh mua l\u1ea1i Thiago Alcantara t\u1eeb Bayern Munich, m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan mu\u1ed1n mua l\u1ea1i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1991.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Rafinha va Thiago khong con co hoi sat canh ben canh nhau\" title=\"Rafinha v\u00e0 Thiago kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh nhau\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/rafinha.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Rafinha v\u00e0 Thiago kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh nhau</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nBarca th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 60 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Bayern b\u00e1n Thiago Alcantara. N\u1ebfu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Camp Nou, anh s\u1ebd c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c h\u1ed9i ng\u1ed9 v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi em song sinh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh &ndash; Rafinha.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Vidal, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 Rafinha v\u00e0 Thiago s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh nhau \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 20 tri\u1ec7u euro c\u00f2n khi\u1ebfn c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Rafinha gi\u1ea3m \u0111i \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3, anh v\u1eeba tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eeb Inter Milan theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ra \u0111i \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Sergio Busquets</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sergio Busquets l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, tuy nhi\u00ean anh c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap m\u00ecnh ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh t\u1ed1t c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Vidal se giup Sergio Busquets rat nhieu o nhiem vu ho tro phong ngu\" title=\"Vidal s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Sergio Busquets r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u1edf nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/busques.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Vidal s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Sergio Busquets r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u1edf nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Paulinho h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0111\u1eafc l\u1ef1c cho Busquets trong vai tr\u00f2 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 t\u1eeb xa. S\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha lo l\u1eafng, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1edf ph\u00e0o khi Vidal ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Camp Nou.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile l\u00e0 m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 gi\u00e0u s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh, kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i tranh ch\u1ea5p, anh c\u0169ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m. Vidal ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Sergio Busquets r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u trong vi\u1ec7c h\u00f3a gi\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00ean b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1eeb xa.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1eadm ch\u00ed th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea c\u1ee7a Vidal \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua c\u00f2n v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i so v\u1edbi Paulinho. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, anh t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng 4.3 l\u1ea7n/tr\u1eadn, ch\u1eb7n c\u00fa s\u00fat c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng 1.7 l\u1ea7n/tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c 89%, th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Paulinho ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 2.1 t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 1.7 ch\u1eb7n b\u00f3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2054","checkdouble":"193869"},{"date":"10:40 06/08","title":"T\u00e2n HLV Chelsea chia s\u1ebb kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/31/hlv-sarri-tiet-lo-so-tan-binh-con-lai-cap-ben-chelsea-o-he-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi t\u00e2n HLV. Sau tr\u1eadn, Sarri chia s\u1ebb t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea v\u1edbi m\u1ed1i lo l\u1edbn.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nSarri c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng HLV \u0111\u1eb7t phong c\u00e1ch t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng l\u00e0m t\u00f4n ch\u1ec9, tuy nhi\u00ean Maurizio Sarri kh\u00f4ng t\u00e0i n\u00e0o l\u00e0m kh\u00f3 m\u1ed9t Pep Guardiola gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m h\u01a1n, v\u1edbi h\u01a1n 2 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 c\u00f9ng Man xanh. The Blues \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c 0-2, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Sergio Aguero.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, t\u00e2n HLV Sarri chia s\u1ebb \u00f4ng v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh: &ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh n\u00e0y s\u1ebd m\u1ea5t bao nhi\u00eau th\u1eddi gian. T\u00f4i m\u1edbi t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1ec9 3 tu\u1ea7n, v\u00e0 thi\u1ebfu 6 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t trong tay. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o t\u00f4i, v\u00e0o c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft n\u1eefa.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng g\u00e2y \u00e1p l\u1ef1c t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m, c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh r\u1ea5t d\u00e0i v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng, to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sarri chia s\u1ebb t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea \" title=\"HLV Sarri\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/5/hlv-maurizio-sarri-du-am-tran-chelsea-vs-man-city-sieu-cup-anh-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sarri chia s\u1ebb t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea&nbsp;</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu n\u1eefa v\u1edbi Lyon, v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, thay v\u00ec ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea1y nh\u1ea3y tr\u00ean s\u00e2n t\u1eadp. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang t\u00f4i g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia c\u0169ng th\u1eb3ng th\u1eafn th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Thibaut Courtois, c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111ang th\u00f4ng qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u xin Chelsea cho m\u00ecnh ra \u0111i. \u00d4ng cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n nghe tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u1eeb mi\u1ec7ng c\u1ee7a Courtois, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ph\u00eda CLB n\u1eefa. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c cao nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u. Ngo\u00e0i ra, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd ki\u1ebfn g\u00ec v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng tay c\u00f2&rdquo; &ndash; HLV Sarri chia s\u1ebb t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/choi-mo-nhat-barkley-van-duoc-hlv-sarri-bao-ke-172-193816.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/choi-mo-nhat-barkley-van-duoc-hlv-sarri-bao-ke.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/choi-mo-nhat-barkley-van-duoc-hlv-sarri-bao-ke-172-193816.html\">Ch\u01a1i m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t, Barkley v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Sarri b\u1ea3o k\u00ea</span><br>\r\nHLV Sarri \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng khen ng\u1ee3i t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Barkley v\u00e0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng anh s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Chelsea trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-02-man-city-co-mot-napoli-phien-ban-loi-xuat-hien-172-193804.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/chelsea-02-man-city-co-mot-napoli-phien-ban-loi-xuat-hien.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-02-man-city-co-mot-napoli-phien-ban-loi-xuat-hien-172-193804.html\">Chelsea 0-2 Man City: C\u00f3 m\u1ed9t Napoli phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n l\u1ed7i xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n</span><br>\r\nHLV Maurizio Sarri t\u1edbi Chelsea v\u00e0 mang theo tri\u1ebft l\u00fd b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 \u1edf Napoli. Tuy nhi\u00ean, tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Man City \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00ecnh, h\u1ecd t\u1ecf ra thua k\u00e9m h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n....</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-chelsea-02-man-city-sieu-cup-anh-2018-326-193798.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/video-tong-hop-chelsea-02-man-city-sieu-cup-anh-2018.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-chelsea-02-man-city-sieu-cup-anh-2018-326-193798.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Chelsea 0-2 Man City (Si\u00eau c\u00fap Anh 2018)</span><br>\r\nC\u00fa \u0111\u00fap c\u1ee7a Sergio Aguero \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Man City c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea, qua \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Si\u00eau c\u00fap Anh. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ee9 2 c\u1ee7a HLV...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2053","checkdouble":"193831"},{"date":"09:59 06/08","title":"Real Madrid s\u1eafp bi\u1ebfn Harry Kane \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/28/real-madrid-sap-bien-harry-kane-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Lucas Vazquez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Luka Modric, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha hy v\u1ecdng Real Madrid s\u1ebd gi\u1eef b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Modric c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Real \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1eeb khi chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Real, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Luka Modric \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y. Trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y anh c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Toni Kroos l\u00e0 c\u1eb7p ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Los Blancos. Modric \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia TBN mang v\u1ec1 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u danh hi\u1ec7u.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lucas Vazquez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Luka Modric h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Lucas Vazquez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Luka Modric h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/19/Lucas-Vazquez-phat-bieu-ve-Luka-Modric-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Modric \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t khi \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm nh\u1eefng th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. Ronado \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, anh \u0111\u00e3 r\u1eddi Real t\u1edbi Juventus sau 9 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u00e0 Modric ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u00e1i t\u00ean ti\u1ebfp theo.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia. \u1ede n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh, Tottenham, M.U v\u00e0 Chelsea \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 33 tu\u1ed5i, \u1edf Italia, Inter Milan c\u0169ng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1985.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c2u ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 60 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Modric, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n kh\u00e1 l\u1edbn cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 33 tu\u1ed5i. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec7n b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia, h\u1ecd \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 thay th\u1ebf c\u1ef1u sao Tottenham.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-nham-muc-tieu-200-trieu-euro-thay-modric-180-193772.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Christian Eriksen</span> c\u1ee7a Tottenham n\u1ebfu Luka Modric ra \u0111i, Los Blancos c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi ra 200 tri\u1ec7u euro mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110an\u00a0M\u1ea1ch. Ngo\u00e0i Eriksen th\u00ec Pjanic c\u1ee7a Juventus hay Ramsey c\u1ee7a Arsenal c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Vazquez mu\u1ed1n Real gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Modric</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lucas Vazquez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Luka Modric, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha hy v\u1ecdng Real Madrid s\u1ebd gi\u1eef b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lucas Vazquez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Luka Modric h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Lucas Vazquez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Luka Modric h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/vaz.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Vazquez mu\u1ed1n Real gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Modric</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTrong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, anh \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Real Madrid. Modric th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, anh \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n anh \u1ea5y ra \u0111i v\u00e0o H\u00e8 n\u0103m nay\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cRonaldo \u0111\u00e3 ra \u0111i, Real kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n m\u1ea5t th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m n\u1eefa. T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Modric, \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1edfi anh \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn. Song t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng Modric \u1edf l\u1ea1i, anh \u1ea5y v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft v\u1edbi Real Madrid\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2052","checkdouble":"193833"},{"date":"10:12 06/08","title":"M\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo \u1edf Juventus \"kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp\" \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ebf n\u00e0o?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/muc-luong-cua-cristiano-ronaldo-o-juventus-khung-khiep-den-the-nao.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo thu\u1ed9c h\u00e0ng top th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu ch\u1ec9 so v\u1edbi m\u1eb7t b\u1eb1ng chung \u1edf Serie A, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta c\u00f2n th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 Juventus ch\u1ecbu ch\u01a1i th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu Cr7.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Juventus ch\u1ecbu ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu Ronaldo<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi ra 100 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Cristiano Ronaldo, Juventus t\u1eebng b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u00ean r\u1ed3 khi b\u1ecf ng\u1ea7n \u1ea5y ti\u1ec1n cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 33 tu\u1ed5i. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, Juventus c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng toan t\u00ednh ri\u00eang khi Ronaldo gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin gia t\u0103ng v\u1ec1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 m\u1eb7t t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo toi Juventus\" title=\"Ronaldo toi Juventus\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/muc-luong-cua-cristiano-ronaldo-o-juventus-khung-khiep-den-the-nao.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>M\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo g\u1ea5p h\u01a1n ba l\u1ea7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ee9ng sau t\u1ea1i Serie A.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, Juventus s\u1ebd m\u1ea5t m\u1ed7i n\u0103m 31 tri\u1ec7u euro ti\u1ec1n l\u01b0\u01a1ng cho Ronaldo, con s\u1ed1 c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn n\u1ebfu so v\u1edbi m\u1eb7t b\u1eb1ng chung c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i Serie A v\u1ed1n kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 d\u01b0 d\u1ea3 v\u1ec1 t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh. \u0110\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u1ecbu ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Juventus, h\u00e3y so m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Ronaldo v\u1edbi Gonzalo Higuain, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 hai t\u1ea1i Serie A.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Higuain v\u1eeba r\u1eddi Juventus gia nh\u1eadp AC Milan v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi Ronaldo. M\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng Higuain nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1i AC Milan cao th\u1ee9 hai t\u1ea1i Serie A v\u1edbi con s\u1ed1 9 tri\u1ec7u euro m\u1ed7i n\u0103m, ch\u01b0a b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n ba m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Ronaldo.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Juventus th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb v\u1ec1 ti\u1ec1n l\u01b0\u01a1ng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tr\u1ea3 cho Ronaldo m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng cao v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i so v\u1edbi ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u0169ng cho th\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt kh\u00e1c r\u1eb1ng Juventus c\u00f3 n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Serie A. Trong top 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng cao nh\u1ea5t Serie A hi\u1ec7n nay, Juventus chi\u1ebfm \u0111\u1ebfn 3 c\u00e1i t\u00ean.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 Ronaldo (31 tri\u1ec7u euro), Paulo Dybala (7) v\u00e0 Douglas Costa (6). Hai c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec1u thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf AC Milan l\u00e0 Higuain (9) v\u00e0 Donnarumma (6).&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Juventus c\u0169ng chi ra \u0111\u1ebfn 239.9 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ed5 sung c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean g\u1ed3m Mattia Perin, Leonardo Bonucci, Joao Cancelo, Emre Can v\u00e0 Ronaldo.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Juventus h\u00e8 2018:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/hlv-juventus-real-van-rat-dang-so-du-khong-co-ronaldo-180-193768.html\">HLV Juventus: Real v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-real-madrid-31-juventus-icc-2018-329-193746.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Real Madrid 3-1 Juventus (ICC 2018)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/leonardo-bonucci-khong-xin-loi-sau-khi-tro-lai-juventus-176-193737.html\">Leonardo Bonucci quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng xin l\u1ed7i sau khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/real-madrid-vs-juventus-tran-dau-icc-2018-372-193731.html\">Real Madrid 3-1 Juventus (KT): Los Blancos t\u01b0\u01a1i m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Lopetegui ti\u00eau di\u1ec7t g\u1ecdn B\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/goc-nhin-tai-hop-cuu-den-juventus-kho-lam-nen-chuyen-o-champions-league-176-193654.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: T\u00e1i h\u1ee3p &ldquo;c\u1eebu \u0111en&rdquo;, Juventus kh\u00f3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n \u1edf Champions League</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tan-man/tom-cruise-cristiano-ronaldo-tuoi-tac-co-gi-ma-bat-kha-thi-392-192631.html\">Tom Cruise - Cristiano Ronaldo: Tu\u1ed5i t\u00e1c c\u00f3 g\u00ec m\u00e0 b\u1ea5t kh\u1ea3 thi</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)&nbsp;</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2051","checkdouble":"193834"},{"date":"10:18 06/08","title":"Aaron Ramsey ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn v\u00f2i v\u0129nh Arsenal b\u1eb1ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1ee7ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/6/aaron-ramsey-phu-nhan-voi-vinh-arsenal-bang-luong-khung.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Aaron Ramsey r\u1eddi Arsenal n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 300.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c The Sun \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i. Song ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ramsey \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u00f2i 300.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n \u1edf b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Aaron Ramsey v\u1edbi Arsenal ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 1 n\u0103m, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111ang n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1990. Trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Arsenal, b\u1edfi v\u1eady h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ec3 anh ra \u0111i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 chuy\u1ec7n Aaron Ramsey r\u1eddi Arsenal n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1ee7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 chuy\u1ec7n Aaron Ramsey r\u1eddi Arsenal n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1ee7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/30/Thuc-hu-chuyen-Aaron-Ramsey-roi-Arsenal-neu-khong-co-luong-khung-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ramsey \u0111\u00f2i m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1ee7ng \u1edf b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nRamsey x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Arsenal, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u1ebfu nh\u1eefng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn anh s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, n\u1ebfu Arsenal t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i nh\u1eefng mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a Ramsey \u1edf b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi, anh s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb The Sun, Ramsey y\u00eau c\u1ea7u m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00ean t\u1edbi 300.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n \u1edf b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi. Vi\u1ec7c Arsenal \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00ean t\u1edbi 350.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n cho Mesut Ozil l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales \u0111\u00f2i l\u01b0\u01a1ng cao nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u0169ng theo The Sun, Ramsey \u0111ang g\u00e2y \u00e1p l\u1ef1c bu\u1ed9c Arsenal ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Hi\u1ec7n c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales, trong \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn Chelsea, M.U v\u00e0 Man City.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u00f4m qua, Mirror kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chi-40-trieu-bang-chelsea-quyet-tam-mua-bang-duoc-sao-khung-arsenal-172-193778.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Ramsey</span>, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chi \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1990.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u00c1p l\u1ef1c t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn \u0111ang khi\u1ebfn Arsenal g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1ee7ng cho Ramsey ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ec3 anh ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ramsey ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn v\u00f2i v\u0129nh Arsenal</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Aaron Ramsey r\u1eddi Arsenal n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 300.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c The Sun \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i. Song ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 chuy\u1ec7n Aaron Ramsey r\u1eddi Arsenal n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1ee7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 chuy\u1ec7n Aaron Ramsey r\u1eddi Arsenal n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1ee7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/Truoc-tuong-lai-bat-dinh,-Aaron-Ramsey-phat-bieu-ve-Arsenal-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ramsey ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00f2i l\u01b0\u01a1ng 300.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n \u1edf b\u1ea3n giao k\u00e8o m\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u01a1 quan \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Ramsey kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng cao nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales y\u00eau c\u1ea7u t\u0103ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee9c 300.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo ngu\u1ed3n tin \u0111\u1ed9c quy\u1ec1n t\u1eeb Goal, m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 Ramsey y\u00eau c\u1ea7u \u1edf b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 200.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb m\u00e0 Arsenal ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nK\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi gia nh\u1eadp Arsenal t\u1eeb Cardiff, Ramsey \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 327 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cho Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 ghi 58 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Anh l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Arsenal d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Arsene Wenger, t\u00e2n HLV Emery c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2050","checkdouble":"193837"},{"date":"10:39 06/08","title":"Lucas Vazquez mu\u1ed1n Real gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u00e0y?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/vaz.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Lucas Vazquez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Luka Modric, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha hy v\u1ecdng Real Madrid s\u1ebd gi\u1eef b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Modric c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Real \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1eeb khi chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Real, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Luka Modric \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y. Trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y anh c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Toni Kroos l\u00e0 c\u1eb7p ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Los Blancos. Modric \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia TBN mang v\u1ec1 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u danh hi\u1ec7u.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lucas Vazquez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Luka Modric h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Lucas Vazquez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Luka Modric h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/19/Lucas-Vazquez-phat-bieu-ve-Luka-Modric-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Modric \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t khi \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm nh\u1eefng th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. Ronado \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, anh \u0111\u00e3 r\u1eddi Real t\u1edbi Juventus sau 9 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u00e0 Modric ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u00e1i t\u00ean ti\u1ebfp theo.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia. \u1ede n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh, Tottenham, M.U v\u00e0 Chelsea \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 33 tu\u1ed5i, \u1edf Italia, Inter Milan c\u0169ng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1985.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c2u ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 60 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Modric, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n kh\u00e1 l\u1edbn cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 33 tu\u1ed5i. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec7n b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia, h\u1ecd \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 thay th\u1ebf c\u1ef1u sao Tottenham.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-nham-muc-tieu-200-trieu-euro-thay-modric-180-193772.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Christian Eriksen</span> c\u1ee7a Tottenham n\u1ebfu Luka Modric ra \u0111i, Los Blancos c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi ra 200 tri\u1ec7u euro mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110an\u00a0M\u1ea1ch. Ngo\u00e0i Eriksen th\u00ec Pjanic c\u1ee7a Juventus hay Ramsey c\u1ee7a Arsenal c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Vazquez mu\u1ed1n Real gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Modric</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lucas Vazquez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Luka Modric, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha hy v\u1ecdng Real Madrid s\u1ebd gi\u1eef b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lucas Vazquez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Luka Modric h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Lucas Vazquez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Luka Modric h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/vaz.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Vazquez mu\u1ed1n Real gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Modric</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTrong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, anh \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Real Madrid. Modric th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, anh \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n anh \u1ea5y ra \u0111i v\u00e0o H\u00e8 n\u0103m nay\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cRonaldo \u0111\u00e3 ra \u0111i, Real kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n m\u1ea5t th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m n\u1eefa. T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Modric, \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1edfi anh \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn. Song t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng Modric \u1edf l\u1ea1i, anh \u1ea5y v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft v\u1edbi Real Madrid\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2049","checkdouble":"193838"}]}